      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean you said there's a \"consensus\" that they hurt consumers, but isn't it true that if you don't have them, we just lose all our manufacturing jobs to countries that use cheap labor? seems like a pretty big cost to pay just to keep prices low for a few bucks.",
